name: The Christmas Bundle
description:
The Christmas Bundle

This amazing bundle includes 37 cute graphics for your Christmas projects. You will get watercolor and vector graphics, clip art and seamless patterns.

Clip arts are presented in EPS, SVG, PNG formats. Seamless patterns are saved in EPS and JPEG. All PNG files have a transparent background and are suitable for sublimation.

Ideal for cards, scrapbooking and many other applications.
